text: tamari stri'o manthi je stri'o masikathi nirasa tha'i ga'i hoya, jo tamane sanka hoya to temano samayagalo trana mahina che ane temani pana jene masika avavanum saru pana na tha'i hoya, ane garbhavati stri'ono samayagalo temanum prasuti tha'i jaya tyam sudhi che. Ane je vyakti allaha ta'alathi darase allaha tena (dareka) karya sarala kari dese
